highlights.text: “Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 47 weeks straight.
Sam Smith has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Too Good At Goodbyes” is the highest at #3.
“Déjala Que Vuelva (feat. Manuel Turizo)” by Piso 21 and Manuel Turizo is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 53 spots at #130.
“Walk On Water (feat. Beyoncé)” by Eminem and Beyoncé is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #13.
